  "texts": [
    "IntroductionOver the past decade, the field of artificial intelligence (AI), which aims to emulate human cognitive processes, has undergone significant advancements and encountered intriguing challenges.",
    "Among these, the analysis of subtle facial expressions represents a complex task.",
    "It is observed that the manifestation of a single emotion can vary considerably across individuals, influenced by factors such as ethnicity, age, or gender.",
    "Moreover, the interpretation of an individual's emotional state is subject to contextual variables including lighting, posture, and background.",
    "This paper delves into the intricacies of facial expression analysis in the era of AI, exploring the multitude of aspects impacting the accuracy of human emotion detection."
  ],
